int.10: I started and finished my education in Istanbul. I had the chance to gain experience in many corporate and newly growing companies. Being in newly developing and growing businesses has always excited me more. Although making money is financially necessary in business life, ideas and goals are more important to me. Creative and I also give importance to being solution-oriented. I prefer to spend time with my friends in my spare time. I don't smoke or drink alcohol. I also continue to work on my own e-commerce project.
